- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about natural language parsing tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new approach using hierarchical pointer networks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with developing more effective parsers for natural language processing. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper uses neural networks for parsing. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as pointer networks have been used in computer vision tasks as well.
